title: mShare Windows Mobile v1.10
description:
This Software is completely free, and free to use.
What that means, it doesn't require any fee, monthly commitment, etc.

This software is to be used with your Windows Mobile phone.

It lets you upload files and transfer contacts easily between you phones/pcs/
any device wth browser.

You can check all of your files with no limit in amount of files at your account.
